info: Rating, 5 stars,  · February 2021,  · Stayed with kids
rating_comment: Brother Junayd is a wonderful person and he accepted my request withing a very short time. His property is in the centre point of the city and everything is withing the close proximity. The apartment is big,spacious, open and full of natural light. As it is in the 8th floor,it was peacefull. His father came to welcome us and I must say i was extremely pleased to meet a person with such a pleasant personality. I think a WIFI service will be appreciated by his future guests . Definitely i will tell my friends about his place and people should visit his property. Thanks to brother Junayd once again for having us as his guests.
